---
---
<section class="cta-section" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-inner animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="cta-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Próximo passo</span>
      <h2 id="cta-heading">SEU LIVRO ESTÁ<br /><span class="highlight">ESPERANDO POR VOCÊ</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub cta-sub">
        Fale com nossa equipe. Conte sobre o seu projeto e vamos encontrar o caminho certo para a sua publicação global.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5581999999999?text=Olá!%20Vim%20pelo%20site%20e%20quero%20publicar%20meu%20livro."
          class="btn-primary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013 12.6a19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 011.9 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
          Falar no WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a href="#contato" class="btn-ghost">
          Enviar mensagem
          <span class="btn-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-bd);
    border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    padding: 64px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--sh-lg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--gold-bg) 0%, transparent 65%);
    top: -200px;
    right: -100px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-inner .section-eyebrow { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .cta-inner h2 {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cta-inner { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .cta-actions .btn-primary,
    .cta-actions .btn-ghost { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
